tva:Review.tva:FreeTextReview: So cute..i cant﻿ believe that!
are you crazy or something? or﻿ you are just playing stupid??

My friend told me this video was fake. They painted the cats face with black on one side, then went to﻿ a party store and bought colored contacts. My friend says these people ALWAYS try to scam money, and this is just the tip of the ice berg of their scamming ways.
She's a beauty!!! Love her, I have a cat that has a blaze right up the﻿ middle of her face..

As always, I don't understand why there are dislikes.I have come to the conclusion that there are some people who are just so miserable that they cannot appreciate anything..too bad for them. ..What an unusual and beautiful kitty!﻿
thats one bad ass cat﻿
Is she otherwise﻿ healthy?
Looks fake they missed up on the nose﻿ with the black paint
This is completely FALSE. Where did you come up with this? Besides,﻿ her blue eye is on the orange side.....wasn't aware they made orange shoe polish......
If she has a kitten with the same face I﻿ WANT IT!!! she is looking cool lol.
shes beautiful...i also want a﻿ kittie like dat
I just LOVE this cat!﻿ She is gorgeous!!!!
Star trek comes to mind,Sweet face all the same﻿
beauty﻿
So﻿ adorable.
Such a beauty :)!!﻿
I love﻿ this cat.
Mmmmm﻿ rub that pussay :)
珍百景に出てください！﻿
